                    imap_uid, message_id, subject, from_address, to_address, cc_address, bcc_address,
                    reply_to, date_sent, body_text, body_html, raw_message, flags, size_bytes,
                    has_attachments, folder_name, imap_config_id
                ) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
